OL,3,CMan from Leeds jailed for encouraging
OL,4,Csuicide of 'vulnerable' American
OL,6,FA man from Leeds has been jailed for
OL,7,Fencouraging a 'vulnerable' man in
OL,8,FAmerica to take his own life.
OL,10,FDylan Phelan, 21, goaded Travis Dyer
OL,11,Finto shooting himself in October 2024
OL,12,Fas the pair spoke on the online
OL,13,Fplatform Discord.
OL,15,FMr Dyer, also 21, from Louisiana in
OL,16,FAmerica, was known to be vulnerable
OL,17,Fand struggling with his mental health
OL,18,Fat the time.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
