FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781385841
OL,3,CMan from Leeds jailed for encouraging
OL,4,Csuicide of 'vulnerable' American
OL,6,FThe pair had been talking online for
OL,7,Fmonths, but a police investigation
OL,8,Ffound he was subjected to "sustained
OL,9,Fand serious encouragement to self-
OL,10,Fharm" by Phelan, and two other members
OL,11,Fof an online group.
OL,13,FThe court heard Phelan told Travis
OL,14,Fduring a call: "This is the last time
OL,15,Fseriously, the last time you will ever
OL,16,Ffeel it."
OL,18,FMr Dyer, who was 5000 miles away, took
OL,19,Fhis own life while the video call was
OL,20,Fongoing.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781385841
OL,3,CMan from Leeds jailed for encouraging
OL,4,Csuicide of 'vulnerable' American
OL,6,FThe video recording was sent to Zac
OL,7,FLaw from Doncaster, another gamer on
OL,8,Fthe platform who knew both men.
OL,10,FHe befriended them through an online
OL,11,Fchat group set up for people
OL,12,Fstruggling with their mental health
OL,13,Fbut he was unaware Phelan and two
OL,14,Fother men from America were in a
OL,15,Fseparate group encouraging Mr Dyer to
OL,16,Fharm himself.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781385841
OL,3,CMan from Leeds jailed for encouraging
OL,4,Csuicide of 'vulnerable' American
OL,6,FDescribing what he saw, he said: "It's
OL,7,Fgot Dylan and two American
OL,8,Fparticipants in there, and travis has
OL,9,Fhis camera on and his shotgun and
OL,10,Fthey're just pushing him and
OL,11,Fencouraging him to do it.
OL,13,F"It definitely made me realise the
OL,14,Fpeople you think you know, you don't
OL,15,Fknow and they're capable of things
OL,16,Fthat you never imagined they were
OL,17,Fcapable of."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
