OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781385841
OL,3,CMan from Leeds jailed for encouraging
OL,4,Csuicide of 'vulnerable' American
OL,6,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,7,Fsaid Phelan attended Elland Road
OL,8,FPolice Station in Leeds with his
OL,9,Fparents in March last year to report
OL,10,Fhis involvement in Mr Dyer's death.
OL,12,FHe was taken to the police station by
OL,13,Fhis parents who were told about their
OL,14,Fson's involvement in Travis's death by
OL,15,Fa woman who Phelan had met online and
OL,16,Flater in person.
OL,18,FShe had been told by Phelan about
OL,19,FTravis's death some months after it
OL,20,Fhappened.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781385841
OL,3,CMan from Leeds jailed for encouraging
OL,4,Csuicide of 'vulnerable' American
OL,6,FIn his police interview, he said he
OL,7,Fhad become "drawn to the darker
OL,8,Fgroups" on Discord and "accepted his
OL,9,Fwords were a factor in the suicide".
OL,11,FPolice also found an indecent image of
OL,12,Fa child and other extreme pornography
OL,13,Fimages on his devices.
OL,15,FHe was jailed for six years and four
OL,16,Fmonths for encouraging suicide, and
OL,17,Fmaking and possessing indecent images.
OL,18,FHe was also handed a 10 year Sexual
OL,19,FHarm Prevention Order.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
