PN,36307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781385841
OL,3,CMan from Leeds jailed for encouraging
OL,4,Csuicide of 'vulnerable' American
OL,6,FFollowing the sentencing at Leeds
OL,7,FCrown Court, Phelan's mother Michelle
OL,8,FWalker, said her thoughts and prayers
OL,9,Fare with Mr Dyer's family.
OL,11,FIn a statement she said: "Firstly I
OL,12,Fwould like to extend my sincere
OL,13,Fcondolences to Travis' family for the
OL,14,Fimmense grief and loss they have
OL,15,Fendured. My words will not in anyway
OL,16,Fease their pain.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781385841
OL,3,CMan from Leeds jailed for encouraging
OL,4,Csuicide of 'vulnerable' American
OL,6,F"From the moment I became aware of
OL,7,Fwhat had happened and handed Dylan to
OL,8,Fthe police to this day, my thoughts
OL,9,Fand prayers have always remained with
OL,10,Fthem and it has driven a desire for me
OL,11,Fto never stop fighting to protect and
OL,12,Fkeep all our young family members safe
OL,13,Ffrom this ever happening again online."
OL,15,FIn Louisiana, family and friends of
OL,16,FTravis Dyer told ITV Calendar of their
OL,17,Fanger at what had happened.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781385841
OL,3,CMan from Leeds jailed for encouraging
OL,4,Csuicide of 'vulnerable' American
OL,6,FA close family friend of Travis,
OL,7,FAndrea Benoit, said: "He was alive and
OL,8,Fthen they just encouraged him to end
OL,9,Fit and be so final and then celebrate
OL,10,Fthat.
OL,12,F"It was disgusting. I just can't
OL,13,Fimagine that kind of evil is in
OL,14,Fexistence."
OL,16,FAn earlier tribute from his great-
OL,17,Fgrandmother said life was 'unfair' to
OL,18,Fhim.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
