PN,36310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781385841
OL,3,CMan from Leeds jailed for encouraging
OL,4,Csuicide of 'vulnerable' American
OL,6,FMr Dyer lost his mother and younger
OL,7,Fsister in a car crash, 10 years before
OL,8,Fhis own death.
OL,10,FShe said: "Travie, we miss you.
OL,11,FNeedless to say, I'm so beside myself.
OL,12,FI don't know what to say or how to say
OL,13,Fit. Sweetheart, you were so
OL,14,Funfortunate to have had so many
OL,15,Ftragedies in your young life. It was
OL,16,Ftotally unfair for you."
OL,26,@rD@KOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/11
