PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1781385841
OL,3,CMan from Leeds jailed for encouraging
OL,4,Csuicide of 'vulnerable' American
OL,6,FThe CPS warned those who use online
OL,7,Fspaces to encourage self-harm will be
OL,8,Fheld to account and reiterated the
OL,9,F"anonymity of the internet does not
OL,10,Fplace anyone beyond the reach of the
OL,11,Flaw."
OL,13,FIf you've been affected by any of
OL,14,Fthese issues, these links to
OL,15,Findependent charities and
OL,16,Forganisations may be able to provide
OL,17,Fsome advice and support.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/11
